{"tid":1976695,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疫情下威尼斯水道無船出入　多國空氣質素改善","createTime":"2020-04-17T11:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T11:46:42.000Z","uid":105567,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"258e7de01ce063b4002a934af400d22da2127f3c","tid":1976695,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T11:46:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vPjQ8Q8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvPjQ8Q8.jpg&h=7de922e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n意大利上月 9 日已因武漢肺炎 (COVID-19) 全國封城，全國人口流動暴跌，復活節檔期亦無人外出慶祝。歐洲太空總署本周發佈威尼斯 4 月 13 日的哨兵 2 號衛星圖片，顯示當地著名的水道無船隻活動，歷年未見。而與去年同月 19 日圖片相比，大運河和其他水道都幾乎清空，從威尼斯到穆拉諾島的交通亦近乎不存在。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據意大利新聞社 (ANSA) 報道，復活節期間威尼斯街道和運河幾乎空無一人，只有警察在街道和水路巡邏。同時，封城令整個歐洲的空氣質素變好，尤其是在羅馬和意大利北部的波河河谷 (Po Valley) 。<br />\n<br />\n因疫情造成的類似空氣質素改善情況，也在印度與美國多地出現，其中喜馬拉雅山區近日可從 200 公里外的西北部城市賈朗達爾 (Jalandhar) 清晰眺望，有當地網民形容是近 30 年首次。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vbUtVwK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvbUtVwK.gif&h=fe7228b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/nature/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%A1%9B%E6%98%9F%E5%9C%96%E7%89%87%E9%A1%AF%E5%A8%81%E5%B0%BC%E6%96%AF%E6%B0%B4%E9%81%93%E7%84%A1%E8%88%B9%E5%87%BA%E5%85%A5-%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%8B%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E8%B3%AA%E7%B4%A0%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fnature%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E8%25A1%259B%25E6%2598%259F%25E5%259C%2596%25E7%2589%2587%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E5%25A8%2581%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E6%2596%25AF%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E9%2581%2593%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%2588%25B9%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%2585%25A5-%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%25B4%25A0%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%2596%2584%2F&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU9%2Fuvrtn4HlyTxFQ%2BxjLCx7s%3D&h=09369085\" data-ef-url=\